    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Rime安装配置"><a href="#Rime安装配置" class="headerlink" title="Rime安装配置"></a>Rime安装配置</h1><blockquote><p>本篇以 Windows 系统举例，其他系统及进阶使用可以参考学习<a href="https://github.com/rime/home/wiki">官方文档</a>，文末附有更多参考学习链接。</p></blockquote><h2 id="下载安装"><a href="#下载安装" class="headerlink" title="下载安装"></a>下载安装</h2><p>访问<a href="https://rime.im/download/">官方下载页面</a>，Windows 下载完成后安装过程比较简单，建议自定义用户的配置文件到非系统盘。</p><h2 id="配置"><a href="#配置" class="headerlink" title="配置"></a>配置</h2><h3 id="词库配置"><a href="#词库配置" class="headerlink" title="词库配置"></a>词库配置</h3><p>我这里采用了<a href="https://github.com/iDvel/rime-ice">雾凇拼音</a>，更多使用说明作者在<a href="https://dvel.me/posts/rime-ice/">文档</a>写的已经非常详细，想要学习高阶玩法的可以研究下。</p><p>使用东风破进行安装。</p><figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs awk">git clone --depth=<span class="hljs-number">1</span> https:<span class="hljs-regexp">//gi</span>thub.com<span class="hljs-regexp">/rime/</span>plum<br>cd plum<br>bash rime-install iDvel<span class="hljs-regexp">/rime-ice:others/</span>recipes/full<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>以后更新词库可以使用下面这个命令。</p><figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs awk">rime-install iDvel<span class="hljs-regexp">/rime-ice:others/</span>recipes/all_dicts<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>下一步右键单击 <code>Rime</code> 图标，单击重新部署。</p><img src="https://ghproxy.com/https://raw.githubusercontent.com/zdcxf/blog_pic_bed/master/pic/202306172002899.png" alt="重新部署" class="img-center" style="zoom: 67%;" /><p>然后选择输入法设定，勾选雾凇拼音，选中到下一步选择皮肤。</p><img src="https://ghproxy.com/https://raw.githubusercontent.com/zdcxf/blog_pic_bed/master/pic/202306172006257.png" alt="选择雾凇拼音" class="img-center" style="zoom:50%;" /><h3 id="皮肤配置"><a href="#皮肤配置" class="headerlink" title="皮肤配置"></a>皮肤配置</h3><p>右键单击Rime图标，单击跳转用户文件夹，找到 <code>weasel.custom.yaml</code> 文件，新增如下代码：</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-attr">patch:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">preset_color_schemes:</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">ms_blue:</span> &#123;<span class="hljs-attr">author:</span> <span class="hljs-string">zdcxf</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">back_color:</span> <span class="hljs-number">0xFFFFFF</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">border_color:</span> <span class="hljs-number">0xeaeaea</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">candidate_back_color:</span> <span class="hljs-number">0xFFFFFF</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">candidate_format:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;%c %@ &quot;</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">candidate_text_color:</span> <span class="hljs-number">0x3c3c3c</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">comment_text_color:</span> <span class="hljs-number">0x999999</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">hilited_back_color:</span> <span class="hljs-number">0xD75A00</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">hilited_candidate_back_color:</span> <span class="hljs-number">0xFFD8A6</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">hilited_candidate_label_color:</span> <span class="hljs-number">0x3c3c3c</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">hilited_candidate_text_color:</span> <span class="hljs-number">0x000000</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">hilited_comment_text_color:</span> <span class="hljs-number">0xFFFFFF</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">hilited_label_color:</span> <span class="hljs-number">0x3c3c3c</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">hilited_text_color:</span> <span class="hljs-number">0xFFFFFF</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">label_color:</span> <span class="hljs-number">0x3c3c3c</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">name:</span> <span class="hljs-string">MS_Blue</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">text_color:</span> <span class="hljs-number">0x424242</span>&#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-attr">wechat_green:</span> &#123;<span class="hljs-attr">author:</span> <span class="hljs-string">zdcxf</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">back_color:</span> <span class="hljs-number">0xFFFFFF</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">border_color:</span> <span class="hljs-number">0xeaeaea</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">candidate_back_color:</span> <span class="hljs-number">0xFFFFFF</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">candidate_format:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;%c %@ &quot;</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">candidate_text_color:</span> <span class="hljs-number">0x3c3c3c</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">comment_text_color:</span> <span class="hljs-number">0x999999</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">hilited_back_color:</span> <span class="hljs-number">0x79af22</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">hilited_candidate_back_color:</span> <span class="hljs-number">0x79af22</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">hilited_candidate_label_color:</span> <span class="hljs-number">0xFFFFFF</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">hilited_candidate_text_color:</span> <span class="hljs-number">0xFFFFFF</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">hilited_comment_text_color:</span> <span class="hljs-number">0xFFFFFF</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">hilited_label_color:</span> <span class="hljs-number">0xFFFFFF</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">hilited_text_color:</span> <span class="hljs-number">0xFFFFFF</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">label_color:</span> <span class="hljs-number">0x999999</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">name:</span> <span class="hljs-string">Wechat_Green</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">text_color:</span> <span class="hljs-number">0x424242</span>&#125;<br>  <span class="hljs-attr">style:</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">color_scheme:</span> <span class="hljs-string">wechat_green</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">font_face:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;微软雅黑&quot;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">font_point:</span> <span class="hljs-number">13</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">horizontal:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">inline_preedit:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">label_font_point:</span> <span class="hljs-number">12</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">layout:</span> &#123;<span class="hljs-attr">border:</span> <span class="hljs-number">2</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">candidate_spacing:</span> <span class="hljs-number">20</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">hilite_padding:</span> <span class="hljs-number">5</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">hilite_spacing:</span> <span class="hljs-number">5</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">margin_x:</span> <span class="hljs-number">5</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">margin_y:</span> <span class="hljs-number">5</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">round_corner:</span> <span class="hljs-number">10</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">spacing:</span> <span class="hljs-number">5</span>&#125;<br>  <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;style/color_scheme&quot;:</span> <span class="hljs-string">wechat_green</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>保存退出后，右键单击Rime图标，单击重新部署，然后选择输入法设定，到选择皮肤界面。</p><img src="https://ghproxy.com/https://raw.githubusercontent.com/zdcxf/blog_pic_bed/master/pic/202306180958934.png" alt="选择皮肤" class="img-center" style="zoom:50%;" /><p><code>WeChat_Green</code> 效果</p><img src="https://ghproxy.com/https://raw.githubusercontent.com/zdcxf/blog_pic_bed/master/pic/202306181012786.png" alt="WeChat_Green 效果" class="img-center" style="zoom: 80%;" /><p><code>MS_Blue</code> 效果</p><img src="https://ghproxy.com/https://raw.githubusercontent.com/zdcxf/blog_pic_bed/master/pic/202306181013848.png" alt="MS_Blue 效果" class="img-center" style="zoom:80%;" /><h2 id="实用技巧"><a href="#实用技巧" class="headerlink" title="实用技巧"></a>实用技巧</h2><p><code>v 开头</code>，symbols 字符，可自定义。具体见 <a href="https://github.com/iDvel/rime-ice/blob/main/symbols_v.yaml">symbols_v.yaml</a>。</p><p><img src="https://ghproxy.com/https://raw.githubusercontent.com/zdcxf/blog_pic_bed/master/pic/202307021205458.webp" alt="字符"></p><p><code>u 开头</code>，两分拼字，弥补不知道拼音时的尴尬。</p><p><img src="https://ghproxy.com/https://raw.githubusercontent.com/zdcxf/blog_pic_bed/master/pic/202307021205087.webp" alt="拼字"></p><p><code>rq</code> <code>sj</code> <code>xq</code> <code>dt</code> <code>ts</code>，时间日期快捷输入。</p><figure class="highlight apache"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs apache"><span class="hljs-attribute">date</span>: rq       # 日期：<span class="hljs-number">2023</span>-<span class="hljs-number">06</span>-<span class="hljs-number">18</span><br><span class="hljs-attribute">time</span>: sj       # 时间：<span class="hljs-number">10</span>:<span class="hljs-number">18</span>:<span class="hljs-number">13</span><br><span class="hljs-attribute">week</span>: xq       # 星期：星期日<br><span class="hljs-attribute">datetime</span>: dt   # ISO <span class="hljs-number">8601</span>: <span class="hljs-number">2023</span>-<span class="hljs-number">06</span>-<span class="hljs-number">18</span>T10:<span class="hljs-number">18</span>:<span class="hljs-number">32</span>+<span class="hljs-number">08</span>:<span class="hljs-number">00</span><br><span class="hljs-attribute">timestamp</span>: ts  # 时间戳：<span class="hljs-number">1687054724</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>至此就可以愉快的使用了，如果想继续折腾进阶使用，请参考以下学习链接。</p><h2 id="更多教程"><a href="#更多教程" class="headerlink" title="更多教程"></a>更多教程</h2><p>快速上手：<a href="https://immmmm.com/hi-rime/">Hi，Rime</a></p><p>脚本自动部署：<a href="https://github.com/Mark24Code/rime-auto-deploy">Rime auto deploy</a></p><p>多平台安装配置及进阶配置：<a href="https://www.mintimate.cn/2023/03/18/rimeQuickInit/#Rime">跨平台的开源输入法Rime定制指南(mintimate.cn)</a></p><p><a href="https://chenhe.me/post/oh-my-rime/">Rime&#x2F;小狼豪&#x2F;鼠须管 输入法配置记 (chenhe.me)</a></p><p>Windows ： <a href="https://eallion.com/weasel/">Windows 安装 Rime 小狼毫五笔拼音输入法</a> 。</p><p>iPhone ： <a href="https://github.com/imfuxiao/Hamster">imfuxiao&#x2F;Hamster</a> （<a href="https://github.com/imfuxiao/Hamster/wiki/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%AF%BC%E5%85%A5%22%E9%9B%BE%E6%B7%9E%E6%8B%BC%E9%9F%B3%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%22">如何导入 “雾淞拼音输入方案”</a>）</p><p>多端安装教程：<a href="https://x.geekbb.ml/RIME">从 macOS 到 iPhone 全面拥抱 RIME 输入法 - Geek</a></p><p>雾凇拼音仓库： <a href="https://github.com/iDvel/rime-ice">iDvel&#x2F;rime-ice: Rime 配置：雾凇拼音 | 长期维护的简体词库</a></p><p>配置详解：<a href="https://ssnhd.com/2022/01/06/rime/">鼠须管输入法配置详解 - 三十年河東</a></p>]]></content>
    
    
